constraints.additionalInfo: No minimum deposit required to open the account.

eligibility.additionalInfo: The Bankwest Qantas Transaction Account is an account for personal customers who are over 18 years of age.
The Bankwest Qantas Transaction Account is an account for personal customers who are over 18 years of age.
You must be a member of the Qantas Frequent Flyer program to earn and redeem Qantas Points.
There is a limit of one account per person, whether as a single or joint account holder.

fees.name: Honour Fee - Personal
fees.additionalInfo: A $10.00 Honour Fee will apply when one or more transactions overdraw the account, Bankwest elects to honour (pay) the transaction(s) and does not issue an overdrawn notice. The account will be overdrawn if there are insufficient funds, or the applicable credit limit has been exceeded, in order to meet a debit transaction (including cheques, direct debits and/or periodical payments). Bankwest will only charge one Honour Fee per account, per-day.

fees.name: Overseas ATM Fee
fees.additionalInfo: No Bankwest-charged overseas ATM access fees. The overseas bank may charge a fee for using their ATM.

fees.name: Outward Dishonour Fee
fees.additionalInfo: A $10.00 Outward Dishonour Fee will be charged to the account where there are insufficient cleared funds in your account to cover a cheque drawn on your account or an authorised debit request made in respect of your account. Bankwest will only charge one Outward Dishonour Fee per account, per-day.

fees.name: Cheque Stop Payment
fees.additionalInfo: Fee to stop payment on an issued cheque. This fee is $25 when payment is stopped on a range of cheques.

fees.name: Inward Payment Fee
fees.additionalInfo: We will charge a fee of $10.00 per transaction for each deposit via the Real Time Gross Settlement System and SWIFT Network.

fees.name: Maintenance Fee

discounts.description: $0 monthly fee if minimum deposit is $2000, otherwise monthly fee is $6.

eligibility.additionalInfo: If the aggregate of deposits made to the account in a month up to close of business on the last business day of the month is less than $2,000, a $6.00 Monthly Maintenance Fee will be charged on the first business day of the next month. This fee does not apply in relation to deposits before the end of the first full month after the account is opened.

fees.name: Duplicate Statement Fee
fees.additionalInfo: Customers requesting a duplicate paper statement to be printed (including faxes) will be charged a duplicate statement fee of $2.50 per statement.

lendingRates.additionalInfo: Variable Overdraft Reference Rate. Applies to any overdrawn amount.
